5′非翻译区雖然不翻譯為蛋白，但可能含有以下[[调控序列|调控序列]]：

* 蛋白质结合位点，这可能会影响mRNA的稳定性或翻译，例如应答[[人類鐵代謝|铁离子]]调控[[基因表达|基因表达]]的[[人類鐵代謝|铁反应元件]]。
* [[核糖开关|核糖开关]]。
* 促进或抑制翻译起始的序列。 
* 5′非翻译区内的内含子与调控基因表达和mRNA出核转运有关。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Genome analysis reveals interplay between 5' UTR introns and nuclear mRNA export for secretory and mitochondrial genes.|author=Cenik, C, ''etal''|url=http://www.plosgenetics.org/article/info:doi/10.1371/journal.pgen.1001366|journal=PLoS Genetics|issue=4|doi=10.1371/journal.pgen.1001366|others=|year=2011|volume=7|page=|pmid=|access-date=2013-07-17|archive-date=2014-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108143056/http://www.plosgenetics.org/article/info:doi/10.1371/journal.pgen.1001366|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[选择性剪接|选择性剪接]]和转录起始位点的变化可以产生替代5′非翻译区。5′非翻译区的多样性会导致其基因表达的变化，这是由选择性5′非翻译区内包含的调控元件决定的。<ref name=Barret>{{cite journal|last=Barret|first=Lucy W|coauthors=Fletcher, Sue & Wilton Steve D|title=Regulation of eukaryotic gene expression by the untranslated gene regions and other non-coding elements|journal=Cellular and Molecular Life Sciences|volume=69|issue=21|pages=3613-3634|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3474909/|accessdate=14 March 2013|date=November 2012|archive-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525175316/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3474909/}}</ref>5′非翻译区内的序列突变或长度改变已被证实与多种人类疾病有关，例如遗传性血小板增多症。<ref name=Chatterjee>{{cite journal|last=Chatterjee|first=Sangeeta|coauthors=Jayanta K. Pal|title=Role of 5'- and 3'-untranslated regions of mRNAs in human diseases|journal=Biology of the Cell|year=2009|volume=101|pages=251-262|doi=10.1042/BC20080104|url=http://www.biolcell.org/boc/101/0251/1010251.pdf|accessdate=8 March 2013}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

